major_00_fool.title: The Fool

meaning.general: The Fool speaks of a fresh start and open-hearted curiosity.
meaning.detailed: The Fool speaks of a fresh start and open-hearted curiosity. At its best, it brings playful courage and optimism. In shadow, it can show naivety or reckless leaps. Advice: step forward, but keep one hand on the rope.

major_00_fool.fact: The Fool is numbered zero, symbolizing limitless potential.

major_01_magician.title: The Magician

meaning.general: The Magician speaks of focused intent and the tools to create change.
meaning.detailed: The Magician speaks of focused intent and the tools to create change. At its best, it brings confidence and resourceful action. In shadow, it can show manipulation or scattered energy. Advice: align your skills with a clear goal.

major_01_magician.fact: The Magician is often shown with all four suit symbols.

major_02_high_priestess.title: The High Priestess

meaning.general: The High Priestess speaks of quiet wisdom and what is hidden beneath the surface.
meaning.detailed: The High Priestess speaks of quiet wisdom and what is hidden beneath the surface. At its best, it brings deep listening and spiritual insight. In shadow, it can show withholding or confusion from silence. Advice: pause, observe, and trust what you feel.

major_02_high_priestess.fact: She sits between pillars marked Boaz and Jachin.

major_03_empress.title: The Empress

meaning.general: The Empress speaks of growth, beauty, and compassionate care.
meaning.detailed: The Empress speaks of growth, beauty, and compassionate care. At its best, it brings fertility and generous support. In shadow, it can show overindulgence or smothering. Advice: create space for steady, life-giving growth.

major_03_empress.fact: The Empress is linked to the planet Venus.

major_04_emperor.title: The Emperor

meaning.general: The Emperor speaks of order, boundaries, and steady leadership.
meaning.detailed: The Emperor speaks of order, boundaries, and steady leadership. At its best, it brings protection and disciplined action. In shadow, it can show rigidity or control issues. Advice: lead with fairness and clear rules.

major_04_emperor.fact: The Emperor corresponds with the sign Aries.

major_05_hierophant.title: The Hierophant

meaning.general: The Hierophant speaks of shared wisdom, rituals, and belonging.
meaning.detailed: The Hierophant speaks of shared wisdom, rituals, and belonging. At its best, it brings mentorship and moral grounding. In shadow, it can show conformity or dogma. Advice: learn the rules, then apply them wisely.

major_05_hierophant.fact: This card is associated with Taurus.

major_06_lovers.title: The Lovers

meaning.general: The Lovers speaks of meaningful connection and aligned choices.
meaning.detailed: The Lovers speaks of meaningful connection and aligned choices. At its best, it brings harmony and heartfelt commitment. In shadow, it can show indecision or divided loyalties. Advice: choose what honors your core values.

major_06_lovers.fact: The Lovers correspond with the sign Gemini.

meaning.detailed: The Page of Cups highlights curiosity and messages in the realm of emotion and connection. At its best, it brings learn and explore with warmth. In shadow, it can slip into immaturity or gossip. Act with learn and explore and stay aligned with emotion and connection.
